data.description: Welcome to this charming 2/1 townhome displaying warmth & character. This cozy property offers more than just a place to reside with an amazing location near restaurants, shopping areas & Nova University. As you step through the front door, you are greeted by an inviting living space w/ wood high ceilings creating an airy & spacious atmosphere. Natural light spills through the doors & windows, casting a soft glow throughout this cozy townhome. The design concept seamlessly connects the living areas. Venture upstairs, & you'll discover ample living space and a sense of sophistication for a bedroom, home office, or personal sanctuary. Step outside to a private yard, for an intimate oasis where you can unwind or entertain friends & family. Bonus NEW Roof being installed!
